      "type": "custom-html",
      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"pt-br\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <title>AI Assistant Banner</title>\n\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:wght@400;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n  <style>\n    * {\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n    }\n\n    body {\n      font-family: \"Lato\", sans-serif;\n    }\n\n    .ai-banner {\n      background: #f7f7f7;\n      color: #000;\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      max-width: 1200px;\n      margin: auto;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 40px; /* controla a distância entre ícone e texto */\n      justify-content: center; /* centraliza o conjunto no bloco */\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n    }\n\n    .ai-banner__icon {\n      /*width: 250px; */\n     /* height: 170px;*/\n      background: #f7f7f7;\n      border-radius: 16px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n\n    .ai-banner__icon svg {\n      width: 80px;\n      height: 80px;\n      fill: #0B58FF;\n    }\n\n    .ai-banner__text {\n      max-width: 300px;\n    }\n\n    .ai-banner__text h4 {\n      font-size: 20px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      margin-bottom: 8px;\n    }\n\n    .ai-banner__text h2 {\n      font-size: 36px;\n      font-weight: 800;\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .ai-banner__text a {\n      display: inline-block;\n      margin-bottom: 18px;\n      padding: 12px 30px;\n      background: #0B58FF;\n      color: #fff;\n      border-radius: 100px;\n      text-decoration: none;\n      font-weight: 700;\n    }\n\n    .ai-banner__text p {\n      font-size: 18px;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n    .ai-banner__icon {\n    border-radius: 10px !important;\n}\n    video.tawk-toolbar-logo {\n    width: 300px;\n    height: 300px;\n    object-fit: cover;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    border: 7px solid #e7e7e7;\n    }\n    \n\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n      .ai-banner {\n        flex-direction: column;\n        text-align: center;\n        gap: 25px;\n        \n        padding: 0px;\n        padding-top: 17px;\n      }\n\n    .ai-banner__icon {\n      /* width: 150px; */\n      /* height: 150px; */\n      border-radius: 16px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n      }\n      \n      video.tawk-toolbar-logo {\n    width: 250px;\n    height: 250px;\n}\n    }\n    \n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"ai-banner\">\n<div class=\"ai-banner__icon\">\n  <video id=\"logoVideo\" muted playsinline preload=\"auto\" class=\"tawk-toolbar-logo\">\n    <source src=\"https://www.macpremier.com.br/img/uploads/aurora.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    Seu navegador não suporta vídeo.\n  </video>\n</div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    <script>\n  const video = document.getElementById(\"logoVideo\");\n\n  // Observa quando o vídeo entra na tela\n  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n    entries.forEach(entry => {\n      if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n        // Quando aparece na tela, começa do início e toca 1 vez\n        video.currentTime = 0;\n        video.play();\n      }\n    });\n  }, { threshold: 0.5 }); // \"0.5\" = pelo menos metade visível\n\n  observer.observe(video);\n\n  // Quando o vídeo termina, volta para o primeiro frame\n  video.addEventListener(\"ended\", () => {\n    video.pause();\n    video.currentTime = 0;\n  });\n</script>\n    <script>\n  document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", () => {\n    const video = document.getElementById(\"logoVideo\");\n    video.load(); // força o navegador a começar a puxar o vídeo\n  });\n</script>\n    \n    \n    \n    <div class=\"ai-banner__text\">\n      <h4>Possui dúvidas?</h4>\n      <h2>AI Assistant</h2>\n      <a href=\"https://tawk.to/chat/652f5a5aa84dd54dc4826169/1hd0fht0v\" target=\"_blank\">Conversar agora</a>\n      <p>Converse com a <strong>Aurora</strong>, nossa assistente de IA, e tire suas dúvidas sobre este produto.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>"
